metadata.name: The Inner Light
metadata.description:
“Don’t you know yet? It is your Light that lights the worlds.”  - Rumi

This work was produced using AI and post-processing, having as a starting point a photograph of me meditating, sitting on Ipanema Beach - Rio de Janeiro - Brazil.

Artist: Stela Narayana 
Edition: 1/1 
Dimensions: 5.376 x 4.096‬px
Software: Midjourney
